==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Audient
<hw>Au"di*ent</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A hearer; especially a catechumen
in the early church.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shelton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
